item.title: Audi TT (MK2) Workshop manual (8J) | 2006 - 2014 Roadster + Coupe
item.description: Audi TT (MK2) Workshop manual (8J) | 2006 - 2014 Roadster + Coupe Audi TT (MK2) service & repair manual provides step-by-step instructions based on the complete disassembly of the machine. It is this level of detail, along with hundreds of photos and illustrations, that guide the reader through each service and repair procedure. Detailed substeps expand on repair procedure information Notes, cautions and warnings throughout each chapter pinpoint critical information.
